files.content:
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "target": "ES2020",
    "useDefineForClassFields": true,
    "module": "ESNext",
    "lib": ["ES2020", "DOM", "DOM.Iterable"],
    "skipLibCheck": true,
    "noImplicitAny": false,

    /* Bundler mode */
    "moduleResolution": "bundler",
    "allowImportingTsExtensions": true,
    "resolveJsonModule": true,
    "isolatedModules": true,
    "noEmit": true,
    "jsx": "preserve",

    "baseUrl": "./",
    "paths": {
      "@/*": ["src/*"]
    },

    /* Linting */
    "strict": true,
    "noUnusedLocals": true,
    "noUnusedParameters": true,
    "noFallthroughCasesInSwitch": true
  },

  "include": [
    "src/**/*.ts",
    "src/**/*.d.ts",
    "src/**/*.tsx",
    "src/**/*.vue",
    "config/**/*.ts",
    "components.d.ts"
  ], // ä»…ä»…åŒ¹é…è¿™äº›æ–‡ä»¶ï¼Œé™¤äº†srcä»¥å¤–çš„æ–‡ä»¶éƒ½ä¸ä¼šè¢«åŒ¹é…
